          "process_md": "***Registration Process for Candidate:***\n\n- Go to the official [CMYKPY website](https://cmykpy.mahaswayam.gov.in/Index.aspx) for job seeker registration and click on “**Intern Login**”.- Use your Aadhaar number as the username for your account.\n- Fill in your full name, date of birth, gender, email, and mobile number.\n- Create a secure password and confirm it.\n- After completing all required fields, submit the registration form to finish the process.\n\n<br>\n\n***Log In Process:***\n\n- Fill Your Aadhar Number as a User Name and Password.\n- Complete your profile details, and fill in the personal, address, qualification, and bank details.\n- Upload the photo, qualification document, birth certificate, etc.\n- Click on “Submit” and apply for the job. \n\n"
        }
